Title: Invader ZIM: Enter the Florpus
Genre: Animation, Action, Adventure, Comedy, Family, Sci-Fi
Director: Hae Young Jung, Young Kyun Park, Jhonen Vasquez
Writer: Jhonen Vasquez, Jhonen Vasquez (creator), Breehn Burns (story consultant), Eric Trueheart (writing consultant)
Actors: Richard Steven Horvitz, Rikki Simons, Andy Berman, Melissa Fahn
Plot: ZIM discovers his almighty leaders never had any intention of coming to Earth and he loses confidence in himself for the first time in his life, which is the big break his human nemesis, Dib has been waiting for.
